headline: Accenture Acquires Ascendient Learning to Expand Learning and Certification Capabilities with Instructor-Led Training and Industry-Recognized Credentials
summary: NEW YORK, May 06, 2025--Accenture has acquired Ascendient Learning, a subsidiary of Axcel Learning, from Alpine Investors, a people-driven private equity firm.
